Text: Readmore …  Dominion Energy Inc (NYSE:D) Director Michael E. Szymanczyk purchased 21,400 shares of Dominion Energy stock in a transaction on Friday, September 13th. The shares were acquired at an average price of $78.85 per share, for a total transaction of $1,687,390.00. Following the completion of the transaction, the director now directly owns 19,541 shares of the company's stock, valued at $1,540,807.85.
